'''Lovnidol''' is a village in the municipality of [[Sevlievo]], in [[Gabrovo Province]], in northern central [[Bulgaria]].<ref>[http://www.guide-bulgaria.com/NC/Gabrovo/Sevlievo Guide Bulgaria], Accessed May 24, 2010</ref>

